snippet.title: Liar's Bar – Will You Be the Last One Standing? | Add to Your Wishlist on Steam!
snippet.description:
Welcome to Liar's Bar! Can you survive in a world where bluffing and deception reign supreme? 🃏🎲

Outwit your rivals in Liar's Dice and Liar's Deck, master the art of lying, and be the last one standing at the table. Every character has a dark past, and each move carries high stakes!

Liar’s Bar launches on Steam on October 2. Don’t forget to add it to your wishlist today!
